World rules - No offline raiding. Only enchanting of weapons is permitted. Stealing is aloud to an extent, if caught you must give the items back. Raiding rules - any raid has to have 4 players or more (6 players allowed in a Faction). For offense 1 piece of diamond armor is aloud for 5 man raids. For defense 2 pieces of diamond armor for 5 man raids. Each raid has to have 4 people on each side. Only operators can have in game player names enabled, Thank you.
